# Dependencies & build artifacts
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.nx
**/.angular
**/.cache
**/coverage
**/test-output
**/tmp

# VCS / IDE
.git
.gitignore
.github
.vscode
.idea

# Logs
*.log

# Secrets — never bake into image
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Compose configs (Docker doesn't need these inside build context)
docker-compose.yml
docker-compose.*.yml

# Tests
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.e2e-spec.ts

# Docs (image doesn't need them; CLAUDE.md kept for reference if any tooling reads it)
docs/
README.md
PROMPT_LOG.md
ASSIGNMENT.md
*.md
!CLAUDE.md

# Local-only tooling
.claude
.husky
